https://www.solidot.org/story?sid=26094	6300
牛津大学授权总部设在香港的“光环”公司<a href="http://www.bbc.co.uk/ukchina/simp/uk_education/2011/09/110920_edu_oxford_furniture.shtml">推出牛津品牌的系列家具</a>。<i>
